'''Furry Hideout is a user-created social world in VRChat — a virtual space designed mainly as a hangout spot for furries and other players to meet, chill, and socialize. It’s one of the more popular “chill” worlds in the VRChat community and has been visited millions of times.'''


The world was created by a VRChat user known as Lt_Shadow (sometimes just called Shadow), who is credited as the author/creator of Furry Hideout


The creator also runs a community (like a Discord and social channels) where fans can follow world updates and events.


It was originally created in April 2021 and has been updated several times since then — including a recent update in October 2025

